00:30:43.939 --> 00:30:46.819
I must examine myself.

00:30:46.819 --> 00:30:50.739
I must prove what is acceptable unto the Lord.

00:30:50.739 --> 00:30:54.019
And let me say, if you were to take time every day this week

00:30:54.019 --> 00:30:59.419
to do these two things, to put the truth this morning

00:30:59.419 --> 00:31:02.299
into practice in your life, and you would take that time

00:31:02.299 --> 00:31:06.659
to honestly and humbly examine ourselves and prove

00:31:06.659 --> 00:31:08.179
what is acceptable unto the Lord,

00:31:08.179 --> 00:31:10.339
when we begin to take that remote control

00:31:10.339 --> 00:31:14.179
and turn on that TV or listen to that thing or wear that thing

00:31:14.179 --> 00:31:17.939
or whatever it might be, we say, is this pleasing to God?

00:31:20.759 --> 00:31:23.739
