00:31:23.739 --> 00:31:26.739
I want to have a conscience that is always

00:31:26.739 --> 00:31:30.859
void of offense toward God.

00:31:30.859 --> 00:31:33.979
That's a powerful statement.

00:31:33.979 --> 00:31:38.699
