00:31:38.699 --> 00:31:40.299
listen, this is how I live.

00:31:40.299 --> 00:31:42.739
I exercise myself.

00:31:42.739 --> 00:31:45.539
I go through the labor.

00:31:45.539 --> 00:31:46.979
I'm striving for this.

00:31:46.979 --> 00:31:47.499
Why?

00:31:47.499 --> 00:31:49.499
Because it's worth it.

00:31:49.499 --> 00:31:51.099
It's worth being in a place where

00:31:51.099 --> 00:31:53.859
there's nothing between my soul and my Savior.

00:31:53.859 --> 00:31:55.779
It's worth being in a place where

00:31:55.779 --> 00:31:59.219
I have a conscience that is always void of offense

00:31:59.219 --> 00:32:02.059
