00:32:23.859 --> 00:32:26.659
there's some things that that offense does

00:32:26.659 --> 00:32:31.499
that impacts our behavior, right?

00:32:31.499 --> 00:32:34.739
Do you avoid the individual?

00:32:34.739 --> 00:32:37.099
Probably.

00:32:37.099 --> 00:32:37.819
Why?

00:32:37.819 --> 00:32:40.899
Because there's something between.

00:32:40.899 --> 00:32:42.999
There's a problem.

00:32:42.999 --> 00:32:45.059
