00:34:12.239 --> 00:34:13.979
Trying to be helpful this morning.

00:34:15.239 --> 00:34:17.579
Because we know what it is when there's an offense

00:34:18.119 --> 00:34:19.979
between us as human beings.

00:34:19.979 --> 00:34:22.979
So why would we think that if there's a conscience

00:34:22.979 --> 00:34:24.819
that's not void of offense,

00:34:24.819 --> 00:34:26.779
why would we think that our fellowship with God

00:34:26.779 --> 00:34:29.220
is gonna be what it's supposed to be?

00:34:29.220 --> 00:34:31.859
It's going to impact us.

00:34:31.859 --> 00:34:34.299
And so it's absolutely essential

00:34:35.479 --> 00:34:39.519
